      • several

        ResultSet several(int amount,
                  Handler<AsyncResult<List<com.datastax.driver.core.Row>>> handler)
        Fetch a specific amount of rows and notify via a handler.

        If remaining amount of rows in a result set is less than desired amount of rows to fetch, the handler will be called with a successful result encompassing just the remaining rows.

        The method should not be used concurrently with others like one(Handler) or all(Handler). This may lead to unexpected result.

        Parameters:
        handler - the handler
        amount - the amount
